Name: Percentage of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed out of all activity executions in the ACM journal review process
Metric: Percentage of 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed occurring immediately after Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' for cases where activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' occurs

Name: Percentage of process variants where Plagiarism Originality Report Completed appears before SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: Percentage of 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' out of all 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Number of times Plagiarism Originality Report Completed is followed by Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded
Metric: Number of 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' activities for cases where activity 'Plagiarism Percent Match Threshold Exceeded' occurs

Name: Percentage of cases where Plagiarism Originality Report Completed occurs without being preceded by Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: Percentage of 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' out of all cases where 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' does not happen

Name: Frequency of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in variants that eventually lead to SW-EIC Accept
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Accept' occurs

Name: Percentage of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed executions that are part of variants containing SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: Percentage of 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Ratio of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed to Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation across the entire log
Metric: Percentage of 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' out of all 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Number of variants in which Plagiarism Originality Report Completed appears more than once
Metric: Number of 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' activities

Name: Percentage of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed activities that occur within 24 hours of Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: Percentage of 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Frequency of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in cases that include at least one reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Reviewer Agreed, SW-Reviewer Declined, or SW-Reviewer No Response)
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' occurs

Name: Percentage of all process instances where Plagiarism Originality Report Completed is executed exactly once
Metric: the average of the function base == 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Number of times Plagiarism Originality Report Completed directly precedes SW-Checklist Completed versus SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days
Metric: Number of 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' occurs

Name: Percentage of variants containing Plagiarism Originality Report Completed that result in a revision decision (SW-EIC Major Revision or SW-EIC Minor Revision)
Metric: Percentage of 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' out of all 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Name: Frequency of Plagiarism Originality Report Completed appearing before any AE assignment activity (e.g., SW-Awaiting AE Assignment or SW-Initial Reviewer Selection)
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' for cases where activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' occurs
